{"tid":1808153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人身保護令 可唔可以對抗濫捕？","createTime":"2020-01-02T07:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T09:02:56.000Z","uid":210558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9c091f56b968d91686853ebb2e0181a4fd5cf4","tid":1808153,"uid":210558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:53:58.000Z","msg":"根據法例：<br />\n<br />\n1)屬以下情況的申請可向原訟法庭提出 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)指稱申請所指名的人是無合法理由而被羈留；並且<br />\n(b)要求就該人發出人身保護令狀。<br />\n(2)申請可由指稱被羈留的人或由任何其他人代為提出，尤其可由聲稱在法律上有權看管某另一人的人提出，或由他人代該如此聲稱的人提出。<br />\n<br />\n仲有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n命令發出人身保護令狀，指示看管申請人的人在指明日期指明時間，將申請人帶到法庭席前，並向法庭核證將申請人羈留的理由；"},{"pid":"dcb5ec43a8c560f05235c2e88cd75204c90f9cf3","tid":1808153,"uid":210558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T07:59:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7daa8abe234c71bc84f9ecfdd5668d44fd99b143","tid":1808153,"uid":210558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:04:26.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0eff49366a6e1bb2653f7ecded60851c4d7d1122","tid":1808153,"uid":210558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"c1f6866801c590848efb9d794ad2f593bf7f2781","tid":1808153,"uid":210558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:11:24.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"727c1ef96eba6b4afc2b6cd45c42087bf1c0ab44","tid":1808153,"uid":210558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:12:56.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"3f0a5e951f06bc3b7d5140d981c8229b768c3be3","tid":1808153,"uid":130797,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:15:06.000Z","msg":"面對野獸<br />\n除左拳頭無野可以保護你"},{"pid":"b867fbb6013d2dd3fc1ccf89895411d6d67b0a11","tid":1808153,"uid":28181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T08:17:16.000Z","msg":"犬謊自己認左sogo出面有唔關事既人，有可疑先可以截查更何況拘捕，立即申請私人檢控告犬謊非法禁錮。"},{"pid":"85e892f21f264a3d5a77870c75198